---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <header class="pt-8 pb-10 animate-fade-in">
    <div class="border-b border-charcoal/10 pb-6 mb-6">
      <p class="label-sm text-clay mb-2">Research Pilot</p>
      <h1 class="heading-xl mb-2">RAY</h1>
      <h2 class="heading-lg text-charcoal/60">Participant Resource Guide</h2>
      <p class="font-mono text-sm mt-4 text-warm-grey">February 12-26, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Navigation for Mobile -->
    <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <a href="#about" class="btn-ghost text-xs border border-charcoal/20">About</a>
      <a href="#safety" class="btn-ghost text-xs border border-charcoal/20 text-destructive font-bold">Safety</a>
      <a href="#privacy" class="btn-ghost text-xs border border-charcoal/20">Privacy</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-ghost text-xs border border-charcoal/20">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="space-y-16 pb-20 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
    
    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="scroll-mt-10">
      <h3 class="heading-lg mb-6">About Ray</h3>
      <div class="body-text space-y-4">
        <p>
          Ray is an AI relationship coach built as part of a Master's research project exploring whether AI can be designed ethically for vulnerable conversations.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ray works with any relationship: romantic, family, friends, work, yourself. It helps you see patterns you might be stuck in.
        </p>

        <div class="grid gap-4 mt-6">
          <div class="glass-panel p-5 rounded-sm border-l-4 border-forest-green">
            <p class="label-sm text-forest-green mb-2">What Ray Is</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li>AI coaching that helps you recognize patterns</li>
              <li>Voice-based (with text option)</li>
              <li>Transparent about being AI</li>
              <li>Available for any relationship type</li>
              <li>Can work with two people at once</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="glass-panel p-5 rounded-sm border-l-4 border-clay">
            <p class="label-sm text-clay mb-2">What Ray Isn't</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li>Therapy or mental health treatment</li>
              <li>Crisis intervention</li>
              <li>A replacement for professional support</li>
              <li>Perfect or always right</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section id="faq" class="scroll-mt-10">
      <h3 class="heading-lg mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">What is Ray exactly?</h4>
          <p class="body-text">Ray is a conversational AI relationship coach. You talk (or type), Ray responds. It's designed to help you think through what's going on in your relationships.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Is Ray a therapist?</h4>
          <p class="body-text">No. Ray is coaching, not therapy. Ray can't treat mental health conditions. If you need professional support, Ray will help you recognize that.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Does Ray remember previous conversations?</h4>
          <p class="body-text">No. For this pilot, each session starts fresh. Ray has no memory of what you've talked about before.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">How long are sessions?</h4>
          <p class="body-text">Sessions are capped at 1 hour. Most sessions run 15-45 minutes. Use Ray as often as you like during the pilot.</p>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SAFETY SECTION (Highlighted) -->
    <section id="safety" class="scroll-mt-10 relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-destructive/5 -mx-6 sm:mx-0 transform -skew-y-1"></div>
      <div class="relative py-6">
        <h3 class="heading-lg text-destructive mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>⚠️</span> Safety Protocols
        </h3>
        
        <div class="bg-white/80 p-6 rounded-sm border border-destructive/20 shadow-sm mb-6">
          <p class="font-bold text-destructive mb-2">Crisis Detection</p>
          <p class="body-text text-sm mb-4">
            Ray cannot help in a crisis. If Ray detects signs of serious distress, it will stop the conversation, provide resources, and alert the researcher.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-warm-grey">
            *If you use Ray late at night and a crisis is detected, the researcher will be asleep and won't respond until morning.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="label-sm text-charcoal">24/7 Support Resources</p>
            <a href="tel:1737" class="btn-secondary text-left justify-start gap-4">
                <span class="font-bold">1737</span> Call or Text (24/7)
            </a>
            <a href="tel:0800543354" class="btn-secondary text-left justify-start gap-4">
                <span class="font-bold">Lifeline</span> 0800 543 354
            </a>
            <a href="tel:111" class="btn-secondary text-left justify-start gap-4 border-destructive text-destructive hover:bg-destructive/5">
                <span class="font-bold">Emergency</span> 111
            </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Research & Cultural Foundations -->
    <section id="research" class="scroll-mt-10">
      <h3 class="heading-lg mb-6">The Research</h3>
      <p class="body-text mb-6">
        This Master's research asks: <em class="italic text-clay">can AI be designed ethically for vulnerable conversations?</em>
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="glass-panel p-6 border-l-4 border-charcoal">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Cultural Foundations</h4>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-clay block">Vā</span>
                    <span class="text-sm">The sacred relational space between people.</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-clay block">Utu Tūturu</span>
                    <span class="text-sm">Enduring collective reciprocity.</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-clay block">Mana Motuhake</span>
                    <span class="text-sm">Absolute data sovereignty.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Why the Tūī?</h4>
            <p class="body-text text-sm">
                Ray's icon is a tūī. Tūī are direct, honest, and have a distinctive voice. They are grounded in place (Aotearoa), beautiful but not precious, and wise but approachable.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Privacy -->
    <section id="privacy" class="scroll-mt-10 border-t border-charcoal/10 pt-10">
      <h3 class="heading-lg mb-6">Privacy & Data</h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="input-field bg-white/40">
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Who sees my data?</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Only the researcher (Lian Passmore). Transcripts are stored securely in ElevenLabs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="input-field bg-white/40">
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Can I delete it?</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Yes. You can delete individual sessions or your entire account anytime during the pilot.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="input-field bg-white/40">
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Is it anonymous?</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Yes. All data is anonymized (participant codes only).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Timeline -->
    <section id="timeline" class="scroll-mt-10 pt-10">
        <h3 class="heading-lg mb-6">Timeline</h3>
        <div class="space-y-0 border-l border-charcoal/20 ml-2">
            
            <div class="pl-6 pb-8 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-clay"></div>
                <p class="font-bold">Now</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-warm-grey">Account Created</p>
            </div>

            <div class="pl-6 pb-8 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-forest-green"></div>
                <p class="font-bold">Feb 12, 2026</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-warm-grey">Pilot Begins</p>
            </div>

            <div class="pl-6 pb-8 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-charcoal"></div>
                <p class="font-bold">Feb 12-26</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-warm-grey">Pilot Period (Feedback after each session)</p>
            </div>

            <div class="pl-6 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-charcoal/40"></div>
                <p class="font-bold">March 1, 2026</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-warm-grey">Deadline to withdraw</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer / Contact -->
    <footer id="contact" class="mt-12 bg-charcoal text-linen -mx-6 px-6 py-12 rounded-t-lg">
        <h3 class="heading-lg text-linen mb-6">Contact</h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-sm">
            <div>
                <p class="label-sm text-white/50 mb-1">Researcher</p>
                <p class="font-bold text-lg">Lian Passmore</p>
                <a href="mailto:lianpassmore@gmail.com" class="block text-linen/80 underline decoration-linen/30">lianpassmore@gmail.com</a>
                <a href="tel:0275668803" class="block text-linen/80">027 566 8803</a>
            </div>

            <div>
                <p class="label-sm text-white/50 mb-1">Supervisor</p>
                <p class="font-bold">Felix Scholz, AcademyEX</p>
                <a href="mailto:mtf@academyex.com" class="block text-linen/80 underline decoration-linen/30">mtf@academyex.com</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
                <p class="text-xs text-white/40">
                    Master of Technological Futures Candidate<br>
                    Project RISE: Relational Insights for Systemic Empowerment
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

  </main>
</Layout>